om/%d6%e1%be%e0/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">轴距</span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">2630mm，</span><a href=\"http://car.bitauto.com/xiaoke/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">逍客</span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">为4315*1783*1606mm，</span><a href=\"http://baike.bitauto.com/%d6%e1%be%e0/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">轴距</span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">2625mm。</span>\r\n			</p>','article.state.normal','普通','visible.false','隐藏',0,'2011-12-16 08:51:05','admin','管理员'),(155,'xingbang.sall.new','新车报价','<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\">\r\n	<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">车型</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">厂家指导价</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">经销商报价</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">优惠幅度</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">其他优惠</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">奇骏2.0 MT 4WD XE舒适版2010款</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">20.78万</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">20.78万</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">5000元</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">3000交车礼</span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-size: